blufixer (1.6.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Theme selector (System / Light / Dark) with persistence in ~/.config/blufixer/theme.
  * Update button in header bar when a new release is available on GitHub.
  * Website link in app menu (replaces old update text).
  * Legal notice section in About dialog (AI assistance disclosure).
  * Modular codebase: monolithic main.c split into 9 modules under src/.
  * Binary distribution tarball (make dist) with pre-compiled executable.
  * All packages now output to build/ with unified naming (BluFixer-{ver}-{arch}.{ext}).
  * RPM binary copied automatically to build/ after rpmbuild.
  * New translation entries: Theme, Legal Notice, Website, update button.
  * Unused translation keys removed, update strings simplified.

 -- Renan Mayrinck <renan@mayrinck.com>  Thu, 21 May 2026 01:13:29 -0300

blufixer (1.5.5-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Async popen migration for Bluetooth version query and device scan.
  * Fix command injection vulnerability via g_shell_quote on usermod.
  * Proper application restart via g_spawn_async + g_application_quit.
  * Scan race condition fix (timeout cancellation + scanning flag).
  * Fix widget memory leaks (g_list_free -> g_list_free_full).
  * Add GError logging on subprocess spawn failures.
  * strtol endptr validation in version parsers.
  * Window validity checks in GTK idle callbacks.
  * Remove dead code (info_body).
  * Pango markup escaping fixes (<> and & in info dialogs).
  * Translation audit: 6 key mismatches fixed, 3 missing entries added.
  * i18n for zenity askpass prompt, atexit always registered.
  * Case-insensitive lsusb scan filter.

 -- Renan Mayrinck <renan@mayrinck.com>  Wed, 20 May 2026 00:00:00 -0300

blufixer (1.5.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.
  * Feature-complete release with CSR fix, ERTM toggle, Realtek/Broadcom
    firmware installation, and Legacy pairing mode configuration.

